    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚工资增长放缓，凸显价格压力缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/australia-s-wage-growth-slows-underlining-easing-price-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚第三季度工资增长放缓，反映出整个经济价格压力有所缓解，并强化了下一步利率将会下降的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/australia-s-wage-growth-slows-underlining-easing-price-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 00:38:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>百达集团在全球搜寻不受特朗普政策议程影响的资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/pictet-favors-india-turkey-and-argentina-as-post-trump-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[百达资产管理公司 (Pictet Asset Management SA) 正在加大对印度和其他新兴市场的投资，这家欧洲基金公司认为这些市场受唐纳德·特朗普政策的影响较小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/pictet-favors-india-turkey-and-argentina-as-post-trump-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在 11 月低点附近企稳，关注需求前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价稳定在本月最低水平附近，在石油输出国组织 (OPEC) 因中国经济放缓再次下调预测后，需求前景成为关注焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 23:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>压力加大，韩国锌业将就存在争议的 18 亿美元股权计划做出决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/korea-zinc-to-decide-on-disputed-1-8-billion-share-plan-as-pressure-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国锌业公司董事会将于周三召开会议，决定是否继续执行价值 18 亿美元的股票出售计划，该计划导致该公司股票遭到抛售，并引发了韩国金融监管机构的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/korea-zinc-to-decide-on-disputed-1-8-billion-share-plan-as-pressure-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 23:02:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市在美国 CPI 公布前跌至两个月低点：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国通胀数据公布之前，亚洲股市跌至近两个月来的最低水平，这可能进一步削弱人们对美联储降息步伐的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 22:45:54 GMT</pubDate>
